summary: This is a recreation of the Morag Tong member, Naryu Virian, in The Elder Scrolls Online
descriptionHtml:
[center][img]https://staticdelivery.nexusmods.com/images/110/48837543-1516747280.png[/img][/center][center][/center][center]'Naryu Virian and her senior member[center] Varon Davel, are the only remaining members of their cell within the Tong. With the Morag Tong presecuted during the second era first from the assassination of the Reman Potentate and from the Dark Brotherhood schism, the members of the guild have gone into hiding and are working from the shadows to try and build connections with the powerful nobles and regain the strength and influence they once had' [i]-[/i] [size=1][i]Elder Scrolls Wikia
[/i][/size][/center][/center][center][/center][center]This a re-creation of the assassin Naryu Virian who was featured in The Elder Scrolls Online[/center][center]Screenshots were taken using the Realvision ENB with all default settings[/center][center][img]https://staticdelivery.nexusmods.com/images/110/48837543-1516747451.png[/img]
